name: MENKO SEASON 1 AVAILABILITY
description:
The battle is heating up, but there is still work to be done, warrior. 

The Menko revolution will not be one to be missed, and it is crucial to seize your opportunity to strengthen your army in preparation for what is coming... 

Menko Season 2 will begin when all Season 1 Menko have been collected, and will see the birth of Menko Mutation tokens, with new ways to evolve your Menko.
